Gujarat Covid-19 Daily Report: 14 June

#Gujarat reported 511 positive cases of Covid-19 and  422 recoveries today increasing State's tally to 23,079 cases including 16,333 recoveries & 1478 fatalities. 
 
Follow @TimesDemocracy for fastest #Covid_19 updates.
